[Olavarria is one of the major beef breeding districts in the country, and off and on has suffered repeated outbreaks. And in such an area of high risk, and high cost, it is very important to make sure that all livestock is regularly vaccinated, even when one has enjoyed a few years free of disease. Yet again, our thanks to Ramon for this update on Buenos Aires Province.

For a map of Argentina showing the province of Buenos Aires, go to http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/americas/argentina_pol96.jpg. For Olavarria, see http://www.fallingrain.com/world/AR/01/Olavarria.html. - Mod.MHJ

